Package com.wasteofplastic.askyblock.events

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ASkyBlockEvent  
    ChallengeCompleteEvent
    This event is fired when a player completes a challenge
    ChallengeLevelCompleteEvent
    This event is fired when a player completes a challenge level
    CoopJoinEvent
    This event is fired when a player joins an island team as a coop member
    CoopLeaveEvent
    Fired when a player is leaves an island coop
    IslandChangeOwnerEvent
    Fired when the owner of an island changes
    IslandDeleteEvent
    This event is fired when a player resets an island
    IslandEnterEvent
    Fired when a player enters an island's area
    IslandExitEvent
    Fired when a player exits an island's protected area
    IslandJoinEvent
    This event is fired when a player joins an island team
    IslandLeaveEvent
    Fired when a player leaves an island team
    IslandNewEvent
    This event is fired when a player starts a new island
    IslandPostLevelEvent
    This event is fired after ASkyBlock calculates an island level and when it sends notification to the player.
    IslandPreLevelEvent
    This event is fired after ASkyBlock calculates an island level but before it is communicated to the player.
    IslandPreTeleportEvent
    This event is fired when a player use for example: /is, /is warp...
    IslandResetEvent
    This event is fired when a player resets an island
    MiniShopEvent
    Fired when a player buys or sells in the mini shop
    ReadyEvent
    This event is fired when ASkyBlock is ready to play and all files are loaded
    TeamJoinEvent
    This event is fired when a player joins a new Team
    TeamLeaveEvent
    This event is fired when a player leaves an existing Team
    WarpCreateEvent
    This event is fired when a Warp is created A Listener to this event can use it only to get informations.
    WarpListEvent
    This event is fired when request is made for a sorted list of warps or when the API updateWarpPanel method is called.
    WarpRemoveEvent
    This event is fired when a Warp is removed (when a warp sign is broken) A Listener to this event can use it only to get informations.
